page.title: 09A SURVEY ON SPARE TIME
page.content: One day my group and I went round the classes in our school to do a survey on spare time.The activities that were popular were{SUNDAY SCHOOL,BOYS {BRIGADE SHIP MATES, GIRL GUIDES, {BROWNIES and the SUNSHINE CLUB. Energetic activities like{Football {and Gymnastics, Karate and Judo}were not so popular. Most of the children went for fun to places like{Disco and Dancing}Classes.
